// Tuple primitive tests (BT-417)
// Tuples are Erlang tuples — immutable fixed-size collections,
// particularly useful for Erlang interop with {ok, Value} and {error, Reason} patterns.

// ⚠️ NOTE: Beamtalk does not currently have tuple literal syntax.
// Tuples are only accessible via Erlang interop or FFI calls.
